DuckDB
  Upstream:  https://github.com/duckdb/duckdb
  License:   MIT
  Copyright: 2018-2026 Stichting DuckDB Foundation

  Most C++ sources and pybind11-based bindings in this directory are derived
  from DuckDB's Python package (`tools/pythonpkg`). Relevant subtrees include
  (non-exhaustive):
    - native/                   (Python <-> native object conversion)
    - numpy/                    (NumPy array wrappers and scans)
    - arrow/                    (Arrow array stream interop)
    - pybind11/                 (pybind11 helpers, GIL wrapper, registered objects)
    - pyconnection/             (PyConnection, ex-DuckDBPyConnection)
    - otterbrix_wrapper/        (PyRelation/PyType/PyExpression, ex-DuckDBPy*)
    - connection_environment/   (framework/object detection, import cache)
    - scan/                     (Python replacement scan)
    - util/                     (box renderer, value conversion utilities)
    - common/                   (exception mapping)
    - components/               (Arrow appenders, table function helpers)
    - main.cpp, pyutil.hpp, conversions/

  These files retain the upstream DuckDB MIT notice as required by that
  license. Modifications carry the otterbrix copyright above.

